name: Assistant Pack 01
description:
An asset library of components meant to help a product (UX, web, w/e) designer communicate with developers, product managers, and themselves.


Assets include:

  • Basic device frames
  • Redline tools
  • Status markers
  • Filler Images
  • Note cards
  • Helpful Unicode to C+P (for better documentation)


This library is compiled from components I regularly use in my own projects. I put it together because it helps me out, hopefully it can do the same for you :)
